05:50.370 --> 05:52.790
You just joined a youth team, right?

05:53.410 --> 05:55.330
I hate receiving.

05:55.840 --> 05:58.790
When you're just starting out,
 the ball doesn't go where you want, does it?

05:59.220 --> 06:00.420
Here, get into position.

06:01.830 --> 06:02.590
Here we go.

06:07.150 --> 06:09.930
Kei, don't try to push it up with your arms.

06:10.390 --> 06:14.600
More like this. Lower your hips, 
and send it out with your entire body.

06:14.600 --> 06:16.050
Try tossing it to me.

06:21.980 --> 06:23.110
Wow!

06:23.110 --> 06:25.530
Receiving is where it all begins in volleyball.

06:25.530 --> 06:27.360
Everything is about keeping the ball in play.

06:27.360 --> 06:29.570
Are you getting along with the other kids?

06:30.490 --> 06:31.450
Yeah...

06:31.450 --> 06:32.370
Liar!

06:32.660 --> 06:34.830
It's written all over your face!

06:44.710 --> 06:45.970
Hello.

06:47.100 --> 06:48.970
U-Um...

06:50.070 --> 06:51.800
Thank you for the other day.

06:53.470 --> 06:54.680
Have we met?

06:56.470 --> 07:03.110
The... other day... a-at the park... The park...

07:00.560 --> 07:03.110
Oh. So, what are you doing here?

07:03.730 --> 07:05.390
Oh, um...

07:06.130 --> 07:08.600
Well, I wanted to play some sport too...

07:08.600 --> 07:11.570
There are a lot of scary guys in baseball and soccer,

07:11.570 --> 07:13.710
