10:15.260 --> 10:20.090
<i>It wasn't like a TV show or movie, 
where there are spurts of blood and heads go flying.</i>

10:20.090 --> 10:22.850
<i>This was far more shocking.</i>

10:23.550 --> 10:25.810
<i>My brother wasn't on the court.</i>

10:25.810 --> 10:27.310
