13:58.750 --> 14:03.730
Ever since that very first three-on-three, I've never been that worried about him.

14:05.970 --> 14:09.920
Though, if Tsukishima starts saying that he wants to quit, 
then I'll panic and try to stop him.

14:09.920 --> 14:11.790
If that happens, I'm trusting you to come help, okay?

14:13.180 --> 14:15.830
I don't know what's going on inside his head.

14:16.330 --> 14:21.750
But we're still growing as a team,
 and we don't know the limits of our skill.

14:22.400 --> 14:27.820
Even if we were to start pressing up against that limit, 
we couldn't help but aim for the very top.

14:27.820 --> 14:30.130
Even though there was no rhyme or reason, we'd keep going.

