15:52.410 --> 15:55.510
Both of your schools are occasionally considered powerhouses, right?

15:55.510 --> 15:56.920
I guess, yeah.

15:56.920 --> 16:01.350
Even if you were able to make it to nationals,
 actually winning there would be difficult, right?

16:01.350 --> 16:03.150
But not impossible!

16:03.150 --> 16:04.920
Now, now, let's hear him out.

16:04.920 --> 16:06.340
This is just a hypothetical.

16:07.290 --> 16:09.890
I'm genuinely curious about this.

16:09.890 --> 16:12.070
Why do you try so hard?

16:12.740 --> 16:16.070
Volleyball is just a club, and maybe you'll get to write,

16:16.070 --> 16:20.430
"I worked really hard in my high school club,"
 on your resume, right?

16:21.520 --> 16:23.460
"Merely a club"?

16:24.780 --> 16:26.920
That almost sounds like someone's name.

16:26.920 --> 16:29.880
Oh, like "Merliah Clubb"?

16:30.390 --> 16:32.720
No, wait. You heard him wrong! He said "just a club"!

16:32.720 --> 16:33.970
Aw man!

