16:44.840 --> 16:46.100
Say, Tsukishima!

16:46.700 --> 16:48.150
Is volleyball fun?

16:51.050 --> 16:52.610
No, not really...

16:52.610 --> 16:55.160
Maybe that's because you suck at it?

16:56.620 --> 16:59.720
I'm a third-year, and I've been to nationals.

16:59.720 --> 17:02.330
I'm better than you. Way better than you!

17:02.330 --> 17:04.080
You don't have to tell me that.

17:04.410 --> 17:08.420
But I only recently started thinking that volleyball was fun.

17:09.840 --> 17:14.220
Ever since my straight spike became usable in matches, I've found it fun.

17:11.800 --> 17:18.760
<b>Straight</b>

