17:15.300 --> 17:18.760
<b>Cross</b>

17:15.300 --> 17:18.760
<b>Cross</b>

17:19.300 --> 17:22.810
I got frustrated and practiced the hell out of straight spikes.

17:22.810 --> 17:23.730
And then...

17:24.380 --> 17:31.260
at the next tournament, I didn't let the same blockers touch the ball at all. I hit it right past them.

17:33.630 --> 17:38.310
Just that one spike made me feel like my time to shine had finally come.

17:45.960 --> 17:48.880
It's all about whether or not you have a moment like that.

17:50.180 --> 17:54.720
What happens in the future,
 if you can win the next match...

17:54.720 --> 17:56.550
None of that matters.

17:57.180 --> 18:05.230
Crushing the guy in front of you and the 
exhilaration of giving 120% are everything.

18:08.810 --> 18:11.690
Well, that's what's it's like for me.

18:11.690 --> 18:15.030
It might not fit for anyone and everyone.

18:15.030 --> 18:20.410
I don't really understand why you say it's
 "just a club," but I don't think you're wrong.

18:20.810 --> 18:24.790
But if you ever experience that moment,

18:25.660 --> 18:29.790
that's when you'll be hooked on volleyball.

